{"tid":1562881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日可唔可以上獅子山陪我慶祝生日[已FC]","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T19:58:25.000Z","uid":238198,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"35022b8bedc1fc0810165c4df6c69d30945a451e","tid":1562881,"uid":238198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的，聽日就係我生日(已FC)，咁啱我又最近又失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴絲可能會話，屌，中秋生日咪同老母過囉，但係我連老母都走埋...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來見到913話上獅子山，咁都諗住有一大班人同我慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係我睇左幾日，熱門一個獅子山po都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日可唔可以有一班巴絲同我上獅子山過生日呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔想中秋註定一人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YB401q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YB401q.jpg&h=6012b163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n28Ga6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn28Ga6X.png&h=00db4cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8JShMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8JShMX.jpg&h=4fcf658e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFC:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFJV7Lt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFJV7Lt.jpg&h=89c82a3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4897b75b2d42a0f4d1888a4bae56311bc1da8ce","tid":1562881,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2